      "summary": "Based on the presented information, a preliminary assessment suggests a Karnofsky Performance Status (KPS) score of 60-70%. This is an educated guess based on the reported fatigue, weight loss, and moderate to severe cough.  A more precise assessment requires a detailed functional assessment evaluating activities of daily living (ADLs).  The ECOG performance status would likely be 2.",
