omprehensive management plan, including surgical resection, chemotherapy, radiation therapy, or a combination thereof.  The patient's comorbidities (diabetes, hypertension) should be carefully considered during treatment planning.  Early palliative care consultation should be considered to address the patient's emotional and physical well-being.",
